description: Using only the highest-quality ingredients and most advanced technology, Paris Religion is serving Denver dazzlingly decadent desserts at delightfully decent prices. This Paris Streetcar will fill you with desire when you glimpse their over-the-top-tarts, ornate Opera Cakes, Parisian style NY Cheesecakes, and other perfectly pristine pastries. Most of their ingredients are organic, carefully sourced, and their fantastic creme fraiche is handmade. You’ll taste the amount of care and craft that goes into this incredible selection of treats, and Paris Religion will undoubtedly make you a believer in their sweets.
name: Paris Religion
